nodes.text: Meeta Cors was an individual who served during the early rebellion against the Galactic Empire in the nascent Rebel Alliance. Around the same time as the mission to Ryloth by the rebels of Phoenix Cell, Cors was in command of the Nautilian as it was being converted into a warship in the rebel stardocks in the Telaris cometary cloud. During its conversion, its construction was hindered by the Ishanna inversion.

In 34 ABY, after The Rebel Files were recovered by the Resistance, Admiral Gial Ackbar wrote on the document on whether his starship, Home One, beat Cors' Nautilian regarding the order of completion. Ackbar's question was later confirmed in writing by Admiral Ushos O. Statura.
